'''Ardys''' is known from the writings of the Greek historian [[Polybius]]. He was an experienced general who commanded the right wing of the army of [[Antiochus the Great]] in his battle against the [[Seleucid Empire|Seleucid]] rebel [[Molon]] in 220 BCE. He distinguished himself in the next year in the siege of [[Seleucia Pieria]].

